### Create container
POST http://localhost:8081/api/v1/containers
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "image": "nginx:latest",
  "command": [],
  "environment": {
    "ENV_VAR1": "value1",
    "ENV_VAR2": "value2"
  }
}


### Start Container
POST http://localhost:8081/api/v1/containers/656879d66e3ea94b2d0988210868f04a848f982deca12a0f2e5b5e9913faad63/start

### Stop Container
POST http://localhost:8081/api/v1/containers/656879d66e3ea94b2d0988210868f04a848f982deca12a0f2e5b5e9913faad63/stop

### Remove Container
POST http://localhost:8081/api/v1/containers/656879d66e3ea94b2d0988210868f04a848f982deca12a0f2e5b5e9913faad63/remove

### Get Container Status
GET http://localhost:8081/api/v1/containers/656879d66e3ea94b2d0988210868f04a848f982deca12a0f2e5b5e9913faad63/status



